# Frontend (`frontend/`)

## Stack

- Vue 3, Vite; entry `frontend/src/main.js`, views under `frontend/src/views/`, game logic under `frontend/src/game/`.

## Unit tests (Vitest)

- Colocated: `frontend/src/**/*.spec.js`
- Run from repo: `cd frontend; npm run test` (or `npm run test` in `frontend` per package.json)
- Prefer mirroring patterns in existing `*.spec.js` files next to the module under test.

## UI and styling

- All UI must follow `ui-design.mdc` (same glob) and [docs/design/11-ui-tokens.md](docs/design/11-ui-tokens.md).
- **Tooltips and in-panel hints** (hover copy, modal helper blocks, no `title=`, equipment quality colors): `frontend-tips-tooltips.mdc` is **alwaysApply** and loads in every chat—follow it together with `ui-design.mdc`.

## Doc sync

- Follow **Doc and Test Sync** in `workflow.mdc`: `docs/design/`, `docs/requirements-format.md`, Vitest, and Playwright when behavior, formulas, or UI-visible output change (or mark N/A with reason).
